rComments: Very boring professor overall, most of his jokes are lame... Impossible to get in touch with him other than to stalk him after class. He might tell you that he thinks his mid-terms will be easy, they're very hard and don't get fooled! Avoid if possible.

He's pretty boring so you have to be really motivated.  His midterms are pretty tough, especially the second one and he ask VERY SPECIFIC information.  Consider learning everything by heart!  He has an e-mail but refused to give it to the students so there's no way to contact him except a public forum wich I think is really bad and unprofessional.
not comprehensible at all and he has too much notes to know for the final and mid-terms, kind of over the medium

Not bad. He does say he's boring in class and he is sometimes but you can tell when he's interested in what he's teaching. It shows. His exam questions were either really specific or really general, hopefully he improves this.

He is just the worst prof when it comes to being bowring! He will actualy declare how monotonous he is during class and than just continue being so. His mid-terms are not fair, he doesn't care about the principles, he wants the details! Very plainly a bad prof!
